Description:
Meet Mona, GitHub's original mascot and a symbol of creativity and curiosity! We've made the 3D print files open source so you can bring her to life right at home. Add a touch of GitHub history (and cuteness) to your developer setup.

Grab the files and start printing: https://gh.io/octoprints

#Mona #Octocat #3DPrinting
